items.title: Putin doubles down on demands for Ukrainian territory ahead of talks with US in Moscow
items.description: The Russian president accuses Kyiv of wanting to fight "to the last Ukrainian" - which he says Russia is also "in principle" ready to do.

items.title: Palestinian-US teen freed after nine months in Israeli jail
items.description: Mohammed Ibrahim, now 16, was on holiday from Florida when he was arrested for allegedly throwing rocks at Jewish settlers in the occupied West Bank.

items.title: What we know about the Hong Kong apartment fires

items.title: Firefighters search for hundreds still missing in devastating Hong Kong tower blocks fire
items.description: Dozens of people have died and hundreds remain unaccounted for after Wednesday's blaze.
